{"id": "1448323862197440613", "channel_id": "1448323862197440613", "type": 0, "author_id": "702167871144591461", "author_name": "_venush", "author_bot": false, "content": "So we have all these amazing emotes that we can only use in Traphase. It would be nicer if we can use emotes to decorate our profile. And using them in PvE battles.\n\nMy reason for using emotes in PvE battles is because we have the replay feature this anni. Emotes will make watching replays more fun, more memorable and stand out. Replay is an amazing feature so I hope emotes can somehow enhance replay experience too.\n\nAnd of course, more emote usage outside of Traphase battle will encourage players to actually participate in Traphase.", "timestamp": "2025-12-10T14:41:57.304000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 12}], "attachments": [{"id": "1448323862545825864", "filename": "IMG_0103.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 277126, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1448323862197440613/1448323862545825864/IMG_0103.png?ex=69cbdd35&is=69ca8bb5&hm=1e327d49735e558079073f70d7adbec79f17eba2f247948f50f3660f71b8bcd0&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1448323862197440613", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「Answered」About emote usage: Profile decoration and PvE emotes", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361168939622727801"]}
